# 🌐 Interactive Portfolio

## 📌 Overview
This is my personal portfolio website developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It showcases my education, technical skills, certifications, projects, and career goals through an interactive and responsive design.

## ✨ Features
- Responsive Design
- Interactive Navigation
- About Me
- Education
- Skills
- Certifications
- Projects
- Contact Information

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

